<plot>Jack, an escaping lover questions the morality of his actions as he runs away from his pained relationship. Along the way a passing conversation with Lou the Cab Driver further confuses Jack making him wonder if his flight from his love is more a flight from himself. Little does Jack know that his conundrum has been solved for him in his absence in a very final way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?010506</url></doc>
